class.doc:
Command that converts an attached Avro datum to a morphline record by recursively walking the Avro tree and extracting all data into a single morphline record, with fields named by their path in the Avro tree.
The Avro input object is expected to be contained in the {@link Fields#ATTACHMENT_BODY}
This kind of mapping is useful for simple Avro schemas, but a rather simplistic (and perhaps expensive) approach for complex Avro schemas.

